name: THE BEE
description: The weather was hot.  I was at sea.  The bee was floating on the water.  I thought he was dead.  I picked up some sand from the sea floor and brought it up.  When I reached the edge of the beach, it started to move slowly.  I felt he was saying ... I was hot.  I went to the water's edge.  I got caught in the waves, thank you for rescuing me ... and to my surprise it flew after a few minutes.
